                            <comment id="316568" author="egryaznova" created="Tue, 26 Oct 2021 16:21:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the added debug&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32626/28/lustre/tests/recovery-double-scale.sh&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32626/28/lustre/tests/recovery-double-scale.sh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
log &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Using NODES_TO_USE: $NODES_TO_USE and CLIENTS: $CLIENTS&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
NODES_TO_USE=$(exclude_items_from_list $NODES_TO_USE $HOSTNAME)
log &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Using remote NODES_TO_USE: $NODES_TO_USE HOSTNAME=$HOSTNAME&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;shows that for session &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6e63e4d6-ea5d-4ce3-93c9-7176761f6fd8&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6e63e4d6-ea5d-4ce3-93c9-7176761f6fd8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
with Nodes:&lt;br/&gt;
    trevis-205vm10 - Client 1 (2.14.55.29, x86_64)&lt;br/&gt;
    trevis-205vm11 - Client (2.14.55_29_g74c51a8, x86_64)&lt;br/&gt;
    trevis-205vm12 - Client 2 (2.14.55.29, x86_64)&lt;br/&gt;
    trevis-205vm13 - Client 3 (2.14.55.29, x86_64)&lt;br/&gt;
    trevis-205vm14 - Client 4 (2.14.55.29, x86_64) &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the CLIENTS actually set to:&lt;br/&gt;
trevis-205vm10.trevis.whamcloud.com,trevis-205vm12,trevis-205vm13,trevis-205vm14&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/b5cabfa4-e914-4809-831f-5ed50dd7df65/show_text&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_logs/b5cabfa4-e914-4809-831f-5ed50dd7df65/show_text&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i.e. trevis-205vm11 is missing in CLIENTS list.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=adilger&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;adilger&quot;&gt;adilger&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;br/&gt;
can you please advice whom we should address this issue?&lt;br/&gt;
Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
